  "title": "Service Crew $2800",
  "description": "<p>Service Crew</p><p>Working Days: 6 Days</p><p>Working Timing: 7-8 hours/day</p><p>Working Location: Tanah Merah</p><p>Starting Salary: $2,400 to $2,800</p><p>Job Scope :</p><p>•            To be familiar in all service techniques.</p><p>•            To provide service according to procedures and standards established by the F&B Department.  </p><p>•            To assist in all pre-opening / closing duties.</p><p>•            To ensure proper set up of tables and cleanliness of cutleries.</p><p>•            To assist in greeting and seating of all customers.</p><p>•            To be familiar with menu and be aware of current promotions.</p><p>•            To be constantly positive and cheerful and be willing to assist all customers.</p><p>•            To present checks in an appropriate and timely manner.</p><p>•            To obtain feedback from customers and forward them to the attention of superiors.</p><p>•            To report problems in a timely manner.</p><p>•            To be familiar with Club rules, procedures and operating hours.</p><p>•            To carry out any duties that may be assigned to you from your superiors.<br /><br />Interested candidates please call/ WhatsApp me at 88175405 or send your resume to aly@swiftsearchglobal.com<br /><br />Victor Gan (R1550441)<br />Swift Search Global Pte Ltd (EA 18C9495)</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Willie Goh<br />EA Personnel No: R2197853</p>",
